%% Sequence Diagram: Add Jira Ticket to Backlog (FR-002)

sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant CC as Claude Code
    participant TMpl as CLAUDE.md (Intent Detection)
    participant MCP as Atlassian MCP
    participant Jira as Jira Cloud
    participant BL as BACKLOG.md

    Dev->>CC: "Add PROJ-1234 to the backlog"
    CC->>TMpl: Match intent: backlog-add

    Note over TMpl: MCP Prerequisite Check
    TMpl->>CC: Check if atlassian MCP configured

    alt MCP Not Configured
        CC-->>Dev: "Atlassian MCP not configured.<br/>Run: claude mcp add --transport sse<br/>atlassian https://mcp.atlassian.com/v1/sse"
    else MCP Configured
        CC->>MCP: getTicket("PROJ-1234")
        MCP->>Jira: GET /rest/api/3/issue/PROJ-1234
        Jira-->>MCP: { summary, description, priority, status, issuelinks }
        MCP-->>CC: { title, description, priority, status, linkedDocs }

        alt Ticket Not Found
            CC-->>Dev: "Ticket PROJ-1234 not found in Jira"
        else Ticket Found
            CC->>BL: Read current content
            BL-->>CC: Markdown content
            CC->>BL: Append new entry with Jira metadata
            CC-->>Dev: "Added PROJ-1234: {title} to the backlog"
        end
    end
